<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>RADAR — AI Readiness Assessment · {{meta.clientName}}</title>
<style>{{{__css}}}</style>
</head>
<body>

{{!-- ════════════════ COVER ════════════════ --}}
<div class="page">
  <div class="R-cover">
    <div class="R-cover-top">
      <div class="R-cover-radar">
        <img src="{{assets.radarLogo}}" alt="RADAR — AI Readiness Assessment">
      </div>
      <div class="R-cover-meta">
        No. <b>{{meta.reportNo}}</b><br>
        Confidential<br>
        {{meta.editionLabel}} · A4
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="R-cover-mid">
      <div class="R-cover-eyebrow">AI Readiness · {{meta.reportDate}}</div>
      <h1 class="R-cover-title">A six-domain assessment of <em>AI readiness</em> mapped to ISO/IEC 42001:2023.</h1>
      <p class="R-cover-sub">A structured diagnostic of operational, cultural, and governance readiness — with prioritized actions, funding leads{{#if loi25Show}}, and a Loi 25 self-assessment{{/if}}.</p>

      <div class="R-cover-client">
        <div class="R-cover-client-lbl">Prepared for</div>
        <div class="R-cover-client-name">{{meta.clientName}}</div>
        <div class="R-cover-client-sector">
          <span>{{meta.clientSectorLine1}}</span>
          <span>{{meta.clientSectorLine2}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="R-cover-bot">
        <div class="R-cover-bot-col left">
          <div class="R-cover-field-label">Framework</div>
          <div class="R-cover-field-value">
            ISO/IEC 42001:2023 <span class="sep-dot">·</span> <span class="sub-inline">AI Management Systems</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="R-cover-bot-col right">
          <div class="R-cover-field-label">Contact</div>
          <div class="R-cover-field-value">info@nordparadigm.com</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="R-cover-disclaimer">
        This is a diagnostic tool, not a compliance audit or certification. Output language is intentionally precise: it indicates potential gaps, not confirmed compliance.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="R-cover-np">
      <img src="{{assets.npLogo}}" alt="Nord Paradigm">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{{!-- ════════════════ PAGE 1 — EXECUTIVE SUMMARY ════════════════ --}}
<div class="page">
  <div class="R-inside">
    <div class="R-running-head">
      <div class="R-running-head-left">
        <img src="{{assets.npLogo}}" alt="">
        <span class="sep"></span>
        <span>RADAR · {{meta.clientName}}</span>
      </div>
      <span class="pg">01 / {{pad2 pagesTotal}}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="R-section-num">§ 01 — Executive Summary</div>
    <h2 class="R-section-h">Overall AI readiness profile.</h2>
    <p class="R-section-sub">Synthetic verdict drawn from a six-domain assessment mapped to ISO/IEC 42001:2023. Each domain is scored independently; the overall band reflects their weighted aggregate.</p>

    <div class="R-verdict">
      <div class="R-verdict-left">
        <div class="R-verdict-kicker">AI Readiness Band</div>
        <div class="R-verdict-level">{{executive.overallLabel}}</div>
        <div class="R-verdict-pct">{{executive.overallScoreLabel}} overall</div>
      </div>
      <div class="R-verdict-right">
        {{#if executive.strengthHeadline}}
        <div>
          <div class="R-verdict-strength">What you're doing right</div>
          <strong>{{executive.strengthHeadline}}</strong>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if executive.introBody}}
        <div>{{executive.introBody}}</div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="R-summary-eye">§ 02 — Domain Scores</div>
    <h3 class="R-summary-title">Six domains, six scores.</h3>

    <div class="R-summary-grid">
      {{#each domains}}
      <div class="R-domain-card">
        <div class="R-domain-head">
          <div class="R-domain-name">{{name}}</div>
          <span class="R-band {{bandClass}}">{{bandLabel}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="R-domain-bar">
          <div class="R-score-bar"><div class="R-score-bar-fill" style="width:{{score}}%"></div></div>
          <div class="R-score-pct">{{score}}%</div>
        </div>
        <div class="R-domain-iso"><b>ISO 42001</b> · {{iso}}</div>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    <div class="R-foot">
      <div class="mark"><b>Nord Paradigm</b></div>
      <span>info@nordparadigm.com</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{{!-- ════════════════ PAGE 2 — TOP 3 PRIORITY ACTIONS ════════════════ --}}
<div class="page">
  <div class="R-inside">
    <div class="R-running-head">
      <div class="R-running-head-left">
        <img src="{{assets.npLogo}}" alt="">
        <span class="sep"></span>
        <span>RADAR · {{meta.clientName}}</span>
      </div>
      <span class="pg">02 / {{pad2 pagesTotal}}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="R-section-num">§ 03 — Top 3 Priority Actions</div>
    <h2 class="R-section-h">Where to start.</h2>
    <p class="R-section-sub">The three highest-leverage moves drawn from your six-domain assessment. Each pairs the strategic intent with a concrete, low-friction quick win you can run this quarter.</p>

    <div class="R-priority-stack">
      {{#each priorities}}
      <div class="R-priority-row">
        <div class="R-priority-num">{{num}}</div>
        <div class="R-priority-content">
          <div class="R-priority-domain"><b>{{domainName}}</b> · {{domainScore}}%</div>
          <div class="R-priority-action">{{actionTitle}}</div>
          {{#if quickWin}}
          <div class="R-quickwin">
            <div class="R-quickwin-tag">Quick Win</div>
            <div class="R-quickwin-body">{{quickWin}}</div>
          </div>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    <div class="R-foot">
      <div class="mark"><b>Nord Paradigm</b></div>
      <span>info@nordparadigm.com</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{{!-- ════════════════ PAGES 3–5 — DOMAIN DETAIL (3 pairs) ════════════════ --}}
{{#each domainPairs}}
<div class="page">
  <div class="R-inside">
    <div class="R-running-head">
      <div class="R-running-head-left">
        <img src="{{../assets.npLogo}}" alt="">
        <span class="sep"></span>
        <span>RADAR · {{../meta.clientName}}</span>
      </div>
      <span class="pg">{{pad2 (add @index 3)}} / {{pad2 ../pagesTotal}}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="R-section-num">§ {{add @index 4}} — Domain detail ({{add @index 1}} of 3)</div>
    <h2 class="R-section-h">{{#each this}}{{#if this}}{{#unless @first}} · {{/unless}}{{name}}{{/if}}{{/each}}.</h2>

    <div class="R-domain-grid">
      {{#each this}}
      {{#if this}}
      <div class="R-domain-col">
        <div class="R-domain-block">
          <div class="R-domain-block-head">
            <h3 class="R-domain-block-title">{{name}}</h3>
            <div class="R-domain-block-meta">
              <span class="R-band {{bandClass}}">{{bandLabel}}</span>
              <span class="R-domain-block-pct">{{score}}%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="R-domain-block-iso"><b>ISO 42001</b> · {{iso}}</p>

          {{#each actions}}
          <div class="R-action-tier">
            <div class="R-action-tier-tag {{tier}}">{{tierLabel}}</div>
            <div class="R-action-tier-content">
              <div class="R-action-tier-title">{{title}}</div>
              {{#if body}}<div class="R-action-tier-body">{{body}}</div>{{/if}}
              {{#if quickWin}}
              <div class="R-action-tier-iso"><b>Quick Win</b> · {{quickWin}}{{#if iso}} <i>{{iso}}</i>{{/if}}</div>
              {{else if iso}}
              <div class="R-action-tier-iso"><i>{{iso}}</i></div>
              {{/if}}
            </div>
          </div>
          {{/each}}
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/if}}
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    <div class="R-foot">
      <div class="mark"><b>Nord Paradigm</b></div>
      <span>info@nordparadigm.com</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{{/each}}

{{!-- ════════════════ PAGE 6 — FUNDING OPPORTUNITIES ════════════════ --}}
<div class="page">
  <div class="R-inside">
    <div class="R-running-head">
      <div class="R-running-head-left">
        <img src="{{assets.npLogo}}" alt="">
        <span class="sep"></span>
        <span>RADAR · {{meta.clientName}}</span>
      </div>
      <span class="pg">{{pad2 (add 6 0)}} / {{pad2 pagesTotal}}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="R-section-num R-funding-section-num">§ 07 — Funding Opportunities</div>
    <h2 class="R-section-h R-funding-h">Programs you may qualify for.</h2>

    {{#if funding.profileMatch}}
    <div class="R-funding-profile">
      <b>Profile match</b> · {{funding.profileMatch}}
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if funding.eligible.length}}
    <div class="R-funding-eye">
      <span class="R-funding-mark"></span>
      Programs You May Qualify For
    </div>
    <div class="R-funding-grid">
      {{#each funding.eligible}}
      <div class="R-funding-row">
        <div>
          <div class="R-funding-name">{{name}}</div>
          <div class="R-funding-desc">{{desc}}</div>
          {{#if note}}
          <div class="R-funding-note"><b>Note</b> · {{note}}</div>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="R-funding-amount">
          <div class="R-funding-amount-val">{{amount}}</div>
          {{#if verified}}<div class="R-funding-verified"><b>Verified</b> · {{verified}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if funding.investigate.length}}
    <div class="R-funding-eye investigate">
      <span class="R-funding-mark"></span>
      Worth Investigating
    </div>
    <div class="R-funding-grid">
      {{#each funding.investigate}}
      <div class="R-funding-row">
        <div>
          <div class="R-funding-name">{{name}}</div>
          <div class="R-funding-desc">{{desc}}</div>
          {{#if note}}
          <div class="R-funding-note"><b>Note</b> · {{note}}</div>
          {{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="R-funding-amount">
          <div class="R-funding-amount-val">{{amount}}</div>
          {{#if verified}}<div class="R-funding-verified"><b>Verified</b> · {{verified}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    <p class="R-funding-disclaimer">
      Eligibility is indicative only. Program terms and availability should be confirmed with the relevant agency.
    </p>

    <div class="R-foot">
      <div class="mark"><b>Nord Paradigm</b></div>
      <span>info@nordparadigm.com</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{{!-- ════════════════ PAGE 7 — LOI 25 (Quebec only) ════════════════ --}}
{{#if loi25Show}}
<div class="page">
  <div class="R-inside">
    <div class="R-running-head">
      <div class="R-running-head-left">
        <img src="{{assets.npLogo}}" alt="">
        <span class="sep"></span>
        <span>RADAR · {{meta.clientName}}</span>
      </div>
      <span class="pg">{{pad2 pagesTotal}} / {{pad2 pagesTotal}}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="R-section-num">§ 08 — Loi 25 — Quebec Privacy Obligations</div>
    <h2 class="R-section-h">Privacy readiness self-assessment.</h2>

    <div class="R-loi25-verdict">
      <div>
        <div class="R-verdict-kicker">Loi 25 Readiness</div>
        <div class="R-loi25-pct">{{loi25.scoreInt}}%</div>
        <div class="R-loi25-band">{{loi25.bandLabel}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="R-loi25-verdict-body">
        {{loi25.verdictBody}}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="R-loi25-grid">
      {{#each loi25.questions}}
      <div class="R-loi25-q">
        <div class="R-loi25-q-head">
          <div>
            <div class="R-loi25-q-num">{{num}} · {{shortLabel}}</div>
            <div class="R-loi25-q-title">{{title}}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="R-loi25-q-score">
            {{#times scoreOnPips}}<span class="R-pip on"></span>{{/times}}{{#times scoreOffPips}}<span class="R-pip"></span>{{/times}}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="R-loi25-q-iso"><b>Loi 25</b> · {{article}} · Score {{score}}/4</div>
        {{#if responseText}}<div class="R-loi25-q-resp"><b>Your response</b> · {{responseText}}</div>{{/if}}
        {{#if nextStep}}<div class="R-loi25-q-step">{{nextStep}}</div>{{/if}}
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>

    <p class="R-loi25-disclaimer">
      This is a self-assessment, not legal advice. Loi 25 compliance is a legal judgement that requires review by a qualified privacy specialist. Output language is intentionally precise: "indicates potential gaps," not "confirms compliance." This assessment is mapped to ISO/IEC 42001:2023, the international standard for AI Management Systems.
    </p>

    <div class="R-foot">
      <div class="mark"><b>Nord Paradigm · info@nordparadigm.com</b></div>
      <span>nordparadigm.com</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{{/if}}

</body>
</html>
